              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">17186:1117862</code> &mdash; Component Set: Slider</li>
